# VHS tape for the README recording (https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs).
# Regenerate with:  make gif    (needs vhs, ffmpeg, and ttyd installed, plus a key in .env)
# It runs the cheap quick demo, so the recording is a real live run, not a staged screencast.

Output docs/demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 820
Set Padding 18

Type "make demo-quick"
Enter
Sleep 75s
